  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have mastered most forms of Genjutsu. At 13th level, you immediately gain one of the following features. You gain a second one at 20th level. </p><ul><li><p><strong>Greater Mastery</strong>: Creatures who's saving throw result is 2 or more, lower than your Save DC, is treated as if they Critically Failed. </p></li><li><p><strong>Higher Understanding</strong>: Creature must beat your save DC by 10 or more to be treated as if they Critically succeeded on a Genjutsu you cast. </p></li><li><p><strong>Subdued Illusion</strong>: The Genjutsu Specialists is able to increase the Illusion check DC made to identify his Genjutsu by 5. </p></li><li><p><strong>Genjutsu Flow</strong>: The Genjutsu Specialist doubles the range of Genjutsu they cast. Genjutsu with \"Touch\" range now have a range of 30 feet.</p></li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
